*''[[Mass (Stravinsky)|Mass]]'' (1948)
*''[[Cantata (Stravinsky)|Cantata]]'' for soprano, tenor, female voices, 2 flutes, oboe, English horn, cello (1953-1954)
*''[[Canticum Sacrum]]'' (1955)
*''[[Threni]]'' (1958)
*''[[A Sermon, a Narrative and a Prayer]]'' (1961)
*''[[Abraham and Isaac]]'' (1963)
*''[[Introitus (Stravinsky)|Introitus]]'' (1965)
*''[[Requiem Canticles]]'' (1966)

