*''[[The Nightingale|Le rossignol]] (The Nightingale)'' (1914)
*''[[Renard (Stravinsky)|Renard]], [[burlesque]]'' for 4 [[Pantomime (theatre)|Pantomime]]s and Chamber Orchestra (1916)(see also Ballets)
*''[[Mavra]]'' (1922)
*''[[Oedipus rex (opera)|Oedipus rex]]'' (1927)
